        <item>
            <title>全球最細吸塵機破健力士紀錄   印度學生用一支原子筆製作</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/indian-student-builds-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-using-a-pen/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=indian-student-builds-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-using-a-pen</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/indian-student-builds-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-using-a-pen/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 10:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健力士]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健力士世界紀錄]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[吸塵機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262499</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日一名 23 歲印度工程學學生以一支原子筆為基礎，成功製造出全球最細的吸塵器，打破了健力士世界紀錄。這「部」全球最細的吸塵機展示瞭如何利用日常物品轉化為實用科技產品，為環保和科技界注入了全新靈感。</p><p>根據健力士世界紀錄的量度方式（手柄、電源線等不計算在內），這款吸塵器主體最短軸僅有 0.65 釐米長，比手指尾指甲更細。不要看它機仔細細，其設有吸入口和塵埃收集裝置，並可透過 USB 供電。這款吸塵器設計雖然輕巧，但功能強大，能有效清理微塵和碎屑，特別適合清潔鍵盤及汽車內飾等狹窄空間。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912152504-694x454.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="454" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912152504-694x454.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912152504.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2024/9/indian-student-builds-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-using-a-pen">Guiness World Records</a></p><p>憑一支原子筆打破全球最細吸塵機世界紀錄的學生名叫 Tapala Nadamuni ，其表示他目標是透過日常用品，設計新穎又實用的工具。Tapala Nadamuni 指，雖然吸塵器外形看似平平無奇，但其內部機制經過精心設計，實際使用時具有一定清潔能力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912153842-694x454.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="454" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912153842-694x454.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912153842.jpg 1278w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2024/9/indian-student-builds-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-using-a-pen">Guiness World Records</a></p><p>根據健力士世界紀錄對吸塵機的定義，吸塵機應為一種透過內部負壓產生吸力以拾取碎片的電動裝置（ an electrically powered device which picks up debris with suction resulting from a negative internal pressure.）Tapala Nadamuni 表示，設計時遇到的難題是怎樣在如此細小的機身產生足夠吸起碎片的吸力。Tapala Nadamuni 打破世界紀錄的吸塵機主要材料為一支普通可換芯原子筆，另外加入了些少塑膠和金屬，總成本約為 2 萬印度盧比（約港幣 1,856 元）。吸塵機內設由 4 Volt 震動摩打推動的微型風扇，以產生吸力。當用家連接電源後，吸塵機會隨即啟動。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262515" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912154525-694x456.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="456" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912154525-694x456.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240912154525.jpg 1275w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2024/9/indian-student-builds-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-using-a-pen">Guiness World Records</a></p><p>健力士世界紀錄審核團隊最終確認這款吸塵器是目前「全球最細吸塵機」。據印度媒體報道，Tapala Nadamuni 希望他的發明能鼓勵更多人參與創新設計，並展示如何以低成本實現高效能的成果。Tapala Nadamuni 又指，發明不一定需要依賴昂貴的材料或複雜的技術，只要運用創意，日常物品亦能轉變成驚人的工具。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2024/9/indian-student-builds-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-using-a-pen">Guiness World Records</a>、<a href="https://www.ndtv.com/offbeat/indian-student-makes-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-from-a-simple-pen-6504476">NDTV</a>、<a href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/indian-student-sets-guinness-world-record-with-the-worlds-smallest-vacuum-leaner/articleshow/113168956.cms">Times of India</a>、<a href="https://www.newindianexpress.com/nation/2024/Sep/09/23-year-old-indian-student-sets-guinness-world-record-with-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner">Indian Express</a></p><div class="post-article-block"><div class="block-main"><header><div class="line-1"></div></header></div></div><div class="post-article-block featured-image-block"></div><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/youtubers-built-6-ft-tall-working-replica-of-iphone-15-pro-max/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">破健力士世界紀錄   YouTuber 自製 6 呎高 iPhone 15 Pro</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/16/ibrahim-al-nasser/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">成功連接 444 部遊戲機至單一電視　沙特男子創造新健力士世界紀錄</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/indian-student-builds-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-using-a-pen/fun-tech/">全球最細吸塵機破健力士紀錄   印度學生用一支原子筆製作</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/indian-student-builds-worlds-smallest-vacuum-cleaner-using-a-pen/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>調查指 90% 玩家認為 PS5 Pro 售價過高　外媒：只有 15% 人想買</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/polls-show-only-around-10-15-percent-plan-to-buy-ps5-pro-most-consider-it-too-expensive/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=polls-show-only-around-10-15-percent-plan-to-buy-ps5-pro-most-consider-it-too-expensive</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/polls-show-only-around-10-15-percent-plan-to-buy-ps5-pro-most-consider-it-too-expensive/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 09:00:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY PlayStation 5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony PS5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262503</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 最近公佈了 PlayStation 5 Pro（PS5 Pro） 的香港售價，售價定為港幣 5,780 元。部分玩家認為 PS5 Pro 的定價偏高，難以接受。根據 IGN 的調查顯示，只有約 10-15% 的玩家有意購買這款升級版主機，而大多數玩家則對其價格和性價比持保留態度。玩家普遍認為，現有 PS5 已經能夠滿足絕大多數遊戲需求，PS5 Pro 即使效能有所提升，仍無法彌補價格升幅。</p><p>PS5 Pro 在硬件方面進行了多項升級，包括支援 Wi-Fi 7、VRR 和 8K 顯示，使用比 PS5 更先進的 GPU，運算單元比 PS5 多 67%，記憶體速度也快了 28%，使遊戲渲染速度整體提升 45%。然而上述改進對一些玩家來説並不足以合理化其價格。IGN 的調查數據顯示，雖然部分玩家對新主機的硬件提升表示興奮，但絕大多數玩家並不打算升級 PS5 Pro。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240910at-1-694x468.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="468" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240910at-1-694x468.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240910at-1.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲逾 9 成投票玩家認為 PS5 Pro 定價過高，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/polls-ps5-pro-price-reveal">IGN</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240910at-2-694x325.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="325" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240910at-2-694x325.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240910at-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲7 成投票玩家認為 PS5 Pro 售價太高，不會考慮購買<br />
圖片來源：<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/polls-ps5-pro-price-reveal">IGN</a></p><p>美國電子遊戲評論網站《IGN》報道指，不少玩家表示對 PS5 Pro 的價格不滿。他們認為主機硬件升級雖可以提升遊戲體驗，但高昂的價格令普通玩家卻步。許多玩家指會等待主機降價才考慮購買。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protweet172600353-694x339.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protweet172600353-694x339.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protweet172600353.jpg 931w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲IGN 在 X（前稱 Twitter）上發起的投票顯示有 85.7% 投票玩家不會購買 PS5 Pro<br />
圖片來源：<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/polls-ps5-pro-price-reveal">IGN</a></p><p>雖然價格引起了爭議，但 PS5 Pro 對於那些追求極致遊戲體驗的玩家來説，依然具有吸引力。Sony 需要在定價策略和市場需求之間取得平衡，才能讓這款主機在市場上取得成功</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/polls-ps5-pro-price-reveal">IGN</a>、<a href="https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/a/treyalston/ps5-price-expensive-reactions">Complex</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/11/sony-playstation-5-pro-officail-price/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Sony PlayStation 5 Pro 行貨詳情，香港價錢 + 預購及推出日期</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/polls-show-only-around-10-15-percent-plan-to-buy-ps5-pro-most-consider-it-too-expensive/game-channel/">調查指 90% 玩家認為 PS5 Pro 售價過高　外媒：只有 15% 人想買</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/12/polls-show-only-around-10-15-percent-plan-to-buy-ps5-pro-most-consider-it-too-expensive/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
